text: Kristina Tremasova (born on March 13, 1995 in Nizhny Novgorod, Russia) is a Bulgarian ice dancer. Her partner is Dimitar Lichev. She teamed up with Dimitar Lichev in 2009. They participated at the 2011 World Championships in Moscow, ended in 16th place in preliminaries. They also reached 15th place in prelims at 2011 European Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Kristina Tremasova and Dimitar Lichev at the ISU Results Category:Figure skaters Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Bulgarian sportspeople Category:People from Nizhny Novgorod
